-- Pawn is not considered a piece. They are spawned periodically by the King. They deal moderate physical damage and have medium health. (Spawn timer in kings section at the bottom)

-- Pawn’s Advance - Pawn damage is increased by 30% for every Pawn in 100 yds radius

-- En Passant - instant cast, deals low 650 damage in 8 yd radius around the Pawn

-- Bishop has low armor and uses Shadow Bolt as auto attack. His Shadow Bolt auto attack damage is increased by 100% if current threat holder is in 10 yds radius of the Bishop

-- Bishop's Shadow Bolt - 2 second cast, deals 2800-3000 shadow damage

-- Bishop’s Heal - 2,5 sec cast, can be interrupted, heals an injured Pawn for full health

-- Shadow Bolt Volley -3 sec cast, deals 2200-2400 shadow damage aoe in 100 yd radius ((Cast every 15 seconds))

-- Redemption (active only if Knight is dead) - instant, ressurect a pawn with full health (Cast every 30 seconds)

-- Silence (active only if Rook is dead) - silences a random player for 12 seconds, magic debuff (Cast every 14 seconds)

-- When Bishop is the only piece alive, its damage is increased by 30% and he casts Redemption and Silence abilities twice as often.

-- Rook has high armor and slow auto attack speed. Deals heavy physical damage with every hit. ((Attacks every 2.8 seconds))

-- Shield Bash - deals 4200 physical damage, stuns curent threat holder for 5 seconds 

-- Rook’s Advance - charge a random player in 20 yd radius, knocking them back 20 yards and dealing 2555 physical damage

-- Fortify (active only if Bishop is dead) - reduce damage taken by 30% and melee attacks against the Rook deflect 200 physical damage at the attacker (20 second duration, cast every 35 seconds)

-- Siege Equipment (active only if Knight is dead) - periodically spawn a Siege Bomb that explodes after 10 seconds dealing high fire damage in 40 yd radius (can be disarmed by a rogue's disarm trap, if the siege bomb explodes it deals 8500 physical damage within a 30 yard radius) ((Casted every 25 seconds))

-- Knight has medium armor and deals medium physical damage, but attacks fast. (1.3 second attack speed)

-- Knight’s Glory - pawns and pieces in 15 yd radius around the knight get 50% increased attack and casting speed (aura)

-- Glorious Cleave - knight’s attacks cleave, dealing 4800 physcial damage in a cone infront of the caster

-- Trample (active only if Rook is dead) - reduces target’s armor by 50% for 1 minute

-- Ghastly Horseman (active only if Bishop is dead) - spawn a ghastly horseman (can be shackled, turned) (Ghastly Horseman is immune to all damage except holy and shadow, and has the following stats HP:38511, Mana:21444, Armor:4100 and deals 3612-4333 shadow damage) ((Cast every 20-30 seconds))

-- King

-- King is invulnerable and passive as long as any piece (not counting pawns) stands alive.

-- King’s Fury - 5 sec cast, cast whenever a piece (not a pawn) dies, deals 18000 holy damage to players in 100 yd radius (can be los’ed)

-- Summon Pawn - periodically summons a pawn next to the King (Cast every 8-14 seconds at random)

-- King’s Curse - slows movement and attack speed by 50% for 30 seconds (curse) (Cast raid wide every 40-50 seconds)

